text: XHTXA-FM is a Mexican radio station in Tuxpan, Veracruz. It is owned by Grupo FM and is known as Soy FM 93.9. ==History== XHTXA's concession was awarded in 1994 to María del Carmen Jiménez y Betancourt. The station was sold in 1999. ==References== Category:Radio stations in Veracruz
title: XHTXA-FM
